<% frontend = ENV.fetch("FRONTEND_URL", "http://localhost:5174") %>
<% teacher = @resource.invited_by %>
<% teacher_name = "#{teacher.first_name} #{teacher.last_name}" %>
<% accept_url = "#{frontend}/accept-invite?invitation_token=#{@token}&invited_by=#{CGI.escape(teacher_name)}" %>

Hello <%= @resource.email %>,


You've been invited to a learning journey with <%= teacher_name %>


Accept your invitation: <%= accept_url %>

If you didn't expect this, you can ignore this email.
